verbose_text: Smith et al. [XREF_BIBR] demonstrated that miR-143, miR-145, and miR-205 expression levels appear to be elevated in oesophageal squamous mucosa of individuals with ulcerative oesophagitis, while Bus et al. [XREF_BIBR] reported that miR-143, miR-145, miR-192, and miR-194 were upregulated in esophageal epithelial cells upon acidic bile salt stimulation.
